programme.title: The Tennessee guys Adrenaline-Pumped Hunt with Huntech Pro
programme.desc:
Welcome to Episode 8 of Season 4! In this adrenaline-pumped adventure, Dennis Stover leads the pack as they embark on a thrilling hunt with Huntech Pro. Joining him are his brother, Larry, and four close friends, ready for an unforgettable experience in the wild. Dennis takes center stage with a heart-pounding encounter with a Cape Buffalo, showcasing the true essence of the hunt. Meanwhile, Larry seizes the opportunity to harvest a magnificent Cape Buffalo bull, adding to the excitement of the expedition. But the thrill doesn't end there. Lance makes a memorable mark with a remarkable feat, bagging the biggest buck of his life, while the remaining members of the group each have their own remarkable hunting experiences.
Get ready to immerse yourself in the action, adrenaline, and camaraderie as these avid hunters take on the challenges of the wild, leaving behind unforgettable memories and epic tales to share. Tune in to witness the thrill of the hunt like never before!

programme.title: Hunting Whitetail in Ohio (BIG Buck Country)
programme.desc:
Join the Huntech Pro team as they embark on an exciting adventure in the USA, hunting with our friends at Treezyn! In this action-packed episode, Johan and Beulah are warmly welcomed by their friend, Mike Hemby, who kicks off their American journey with a hearty breakfast at Cracker Barrel.
The day continues with a fun and insightful podcast episode with the In Seezyn team before Mike Austin takes over to guide Johan and Beulah to an afternoon hunt near a picturesque lake. Although they spot a buck, they decide it's not the right time to take the shot.
The following morning, the Huntech Pro team enjoys a lively house party hosted by Mike and Suzanne Austin. Then, it's an early start at 4:00 AM as they head to Nashville, Tennessee, for an unforgettable NFL game between the Titans and the Atlanta Falcons, invited by their dear friend Dennis Stover.
The adventure doesn't stop there! The team faces a chilly drive to Howard, Ohio, where Josh Muller from Triplepoint Outdoors invites them for another exciting hunt. Despite the anticipation, no bucks were sighted this time.
Stay tuned for the continuation of this incredible journey in the next episode!

programme.title: Whitetail Redemption in Georgia, USA
programme.desc:
Welcome to the thrilling conclusion of Huntech Pro's Season 4! In this action-packed episode, we continue our annual USA adventure. After facing challenges in Ohio, we set our sights on Kentucky. Despite receiving promising pictures from Justin Wininger of Raw Emotion Outdoors, the changing weather thwarted our efforts.
Our journey didn't end there. We joined Brad Thomas, but instead of deer, we witnessed an epic turkey showdown! With time running out, we headed back to Georgia for one last shot at redemption.
In a dramatic turn of events, Beulah took down a beautiful Whitetail buck at last light. With only one hunting day left, Johan seized the moment at first light, successfully bagging a buck.
Thank you for your unwavering support throughout Season 4 of Huntech Pro! Stay tuned and connected as we gear up for an even more exciting Season 5!
Special thanks to: Justin Wininger - Raw Emotion Outdoors Mike Austin - Treezyn / No Scent Brad Thomas
Stay tuned for more incredible hunting experiences and tips in Season 5!

programme.title: Epic Hunts at BoschNel Safaris
programme.desc:
Season 5 kicks off with an incredible hunting adventure in the Northern Cape, South Africa, at BoschNel Safaris! This episode is packed with intense stalks, challenging terrain, and unforgettable moments in the African bush.
Johan Smit takes on some of the region's most iconic species. One of the toughest hunts was for the elusive Barbary Sheep (Aoudad), testing both patience and skill. He also had a fantastic run, taking down a beautiful Springbuck ram, a stunning common Blesbuck ram, and a magnificent Yellow Blesbuck ram.
Johan was later joined by Kyle Howard, a family member of the BoschNel Safaris team, for a special hunt from a blind built out of lucerne, where he successfully harvested an impressive Kudu bull. To top it all off, Johan put the Ravin R26 crossbow to the test, taking down a Burchell's Zebra in an epic bowhunting moment!
With breathtaking scenery, thrilling hunts, and expert marksmanship, this episode is a must-watch for any hunting enthusiast!

programme.title: Bucket-List Hunts at Ikamela Safaris
programme.desc:
Join us for another thrilling adventure in Season 5, Episode 2 of Huntech Pro, as we head to Ikamela Safaris in the Free State Province, South Africa! Johan and Beulah Smit invited Mike Austin from Treezyn to experience the incredible hunting opportunities Ikamela has to offer.
• Mike kicks off the action by taking down a massive Blue Wildebeest bull on the first afternoon. • Johan checks off one of his bucket-list species, the stunning Hartmann's Zebra. • Beulah and PH Chris Snyman embark on a stalk for a Red Lechwe, but fate presents them with an impressive Impala ram instead. • Johan gets another incredible opportunity to pursue a true African icon – a Cape Kudu bull!
This episode is packed with intense stalks, incredible trophies, and unforgettable moments in the heart of South Africa's wild landscapes. Don't miss out on the action!
